reviewText: YouTube is not a reliable archive of your favorite BigBang music videos but with this you'll always have your copies. A lot of these videos I had never seen.

SSOOOO IN LOVE WITH THIS!!! 

It contains forty-three videos in two discs. A must have for a Big Bang VIP. 

Also contains a thick booklet that has pictures of the k-pop kings from 2006-2012.

You will NOT regret this purchase.
Love it! It comes with a thick little booklet with the video chronology and lots of nice pictures of the band. Definitely a must if you like Bigbang.
I bought this as a present for a friend. She loved it! Highly recommended.
This music video collection has BIGBANG videos and some of the single videos.  It is great!  I get to watch the MVs without buffering or timeouts.  I had already seen most of the videos on YOUTUBE.
